_sText:
EASIER BOTS MOD

This Mod Will Make Bots the Most Stupid Botz in CS Series :) , Making 'em Mean N00bz. Useful for Newbies Who are New to CS:S and Always Die :)
3-4 Bot Names are also Changed.

GAMEPLAY OF N00B BOTZ
Features:
* Decreased Bot Accuracy
* Modified a Few Bot Names
* Increased Bot Reaction Time
* Decreased Bot Aggressivity
* New Bot Templates
* New Botz

INSTALLATION:

1. Unpack (Extract) the BotProfile.db and Place it in:
*Your Counter-Strike Source Dir*\cstrike

2. Now The BotProfile.db Should be in Your cstrike Foler Directory.

IMPORTANT:
Feel Free Givin' a Like and Thanking, This Took Me Days! :D

Have Fun With your N00b Botz. :)
